### Movement Ranking API - Exemplos de Requisições

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Listar Todos os Movimentos
GET http://localhost:8080/movements
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Ranking Deadlift por ID (sem limite)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Ranking Deadlift por ID (top 5)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Ranking Deadlift por Nome
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_name=Deadlift
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Ranking Back Squat por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=2
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Ranking Back Squat por Nome
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_name=Back Squat
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Ranking Bench Press por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=3
Accept: application/json

###

### CASOS DE ERRO

### 9. Erro: nenhum parâmetro fornecido
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Erro: ambos parâmetros fornecidos (XOR)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=1&movement_name=Deadlift
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Erro: movement_id inválido (zero)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=0
Accept: application/json

###

### 12. Erro: movement_id negativo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=-1
Accept: application/json

###

### 13. Erro: movement_name vazio
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_name=
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. Erro: limit inválido (zero)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=1&limit=0
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. Erro: limit negativo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=1&limit=-5
Accept: application/json

###

### 16. Erro: movimento não encontrado por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_id=999
Accept: application/json

###

### 17. Erro: movimento não encontrado por Nome
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rankings?movement_name=Inexistente
Accept: application/json

###

### 18. Erro: rota não encontrada
GET http://localhost:8080/invalid-route
Accept: application/json

###
